title: Jillian Michaels BodyShred Workout
description:
BODYSHRED is an innovative 60-day progressive workout program that consists of 8 S.H.R.E.D. Method workouts and 2 Cardio workouts for a total of 10 dynamic, effective, KILLER workouts!

BODYSHRED will change the way you view fitness. More is not actually Ã¢â‚¬ËœmoreÃ¢â‚¬â„¢. 30 minutes a day of comprehensive, strategically focused training is all you need to get INSANE, accelerated results.

THE WORKOUTS

1. LAUNCH
Start with the basics to build agility, balance, endurance and core strength. Focus is on the arms, shoulders, chest and quads, along with high intensity cardio bursts for a non-stop fat burner.

2. RISE
Increase speed, agility and stamina while focusing on the glutes, hamstrings, biceps, back and calves.

3. FIRE UP
Moderate intensity conditions your cardiovascular system all while delivering an awesome cardio workout.

4. AMPLIFY
Multi-dimensional strength moves work multiple muscle groups simultaneously for maximum calorie burn.

5. ESCALATE
Advanced plyometrics & instability training elevate the intensity.

6. CONQUER
Killer moves tap into your strength, balance and power while intense cardio intervals optimize fat burning.

7. TRIUMPH
Intense supersets elevate your fitness level and optimize accelerated body transformation.

8. IGNITE
Incinerate crazy calories per minute by cranking out this high-intensity, fast-paced cardio workout.

9. ZENITH
Explosive power, higher speed, greater resistance and increased range of motion drive you to your zenith.

10. APEX
Highly advanced bodyweight movements sculpt the leanest physique possible and fire up metabolism
